title: Helparu my leauge launcher won't open.

replies.body:
Are you attempting to run the executable/shortcut and then nothing happens?  If so, it might indicate a problem with the patcher itself.  Make sure to complete all of the steps in our [Patching Issues Guide](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/202969434), which should fix this issue and get you back into the client.

Give me a head sup if you are still experiencing this issue!
